text: Semmiona is a genus of leaf beetles in the subfamily Eumolpinae. It is known from Africa. ==Species== * Semmiona chapuisi (Jacoby, 1900) * Semmiona favareli (Achard, 1914) * Semmiona squameoguttata Fairmaire, 1885 * Semmiona squamulosa (Chapuis, 1874) * Semmiona woodi Bryant, 1941 ==References== Category:Eumolpinae Category:Chrysomelidae genera Category:Beetles of Africa Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
title: Semmiona
